{
  "text": "; Dataset S3 provides a list of the motherenriched proteins discussed below). This enrichment suggests that, quantitatively, the vacuole is unevenly distributed, although it is known that a daughter does inherit the vacuole from its mother in an active process [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
